Bring shortcuts menu:
Ctrl + Alt + S

Intend and format selected (everyhing if nothing selected):
"Reformat Code"
Ctrl + Shift + F

Choose and run configuration:
Ctrl + Enter

Hide run windows:
"Hide All Tool Windows"
Shift + Enter

Find and replace:
Ctrl + F

Comment selected:
Alt + #

Move a statement of code:
Ctrl + arrow up/down

Move a line of code:
Alt + arrow up/down

Delete line of code:
Alt + D

Duplicate a line of code:
Alt + C

Indent line or selection:
Alt + i

Unindent line or selection:
Alt + u
